data.description: Centrally located and just across the street from Lakeside Country Club. This 3 bed, 2 bath all brick ranch home with a sunroom is looking for a new owner. Newer carpet and original wood flooring on the main level. New A/C in 2023, roof 2016, flooring in the sun room in 2021. The house also features a walk up attic with plenty of room to finish for additional living space, two masonry fireplaces that are fully functional, fenced in backyard and a 2 car detached garage. Let's not forget about the fantastic view of the golf course directly across the street. Come take a look for yourself!
